post_text: Congrats to the Tigers XC team who participated in a virtual Bix 7 roadrace through the streets of Tipton. #qctbix7virtual
text: Congrats to the Tigers XC team who participated in a virtual Bix 7 roadrace through the streets of Tipton. #qctbix7virtual

shared_text:
Jill Engels
July 23 at 3:35 PM ¬∑

Tomorrow morning (7/24) shortly after 7:00am the THS XC Team will run a two lap, 7 mile race (some are virtual Bixing) through Tipton starting from the park. They will travel down 9th St, Lemon St, South St, Plum St, 4th St, East St, and back through the park.

If you live along the route or just want something fun to do, please consider social distance cheering for our Tigers. Also if you live on the route, put out your Tiger Nation flag.

If you want to join us in the run, please be at the park by 7am.

GO TIGERS!
